nitro-ng_kmod_build Quickstart
------------------------------

$ git submodule init
$ git submodule update
$ cd linux
$ make oldconfig
$ make prepare
$ make modules_prepare
$ cd ../
$ ./configure --kerneldir=./linux --force
$ make sync
$ make

This will generate x86/kvm-intel.ko and x86/kvm.ko.

Details
------------------------------

This is simply a fork of Jan Kiszka's repo for building external KVM modules and allows you build the nitro-ng modules without having to compile the entire kernel.  This will compile the kernel modules against the latest nitro-ng_kmod master, so the modules are not guarenteed to work on older kernels.

